## 📐 ROI Model

### Step 1 — Baseline Calculation

```
Total Hours Saved = Total Chats × Avg Hours Saved per Use Case
Productivity Value = Total Hours Saved × Hourly Rate
FTE Equivalent = Total Hours Saved ÷ Annual Working Hours per FTE (1,950)
```

