## 🔢 Strategic Value Multipliers

Direct time savings are the floor, not the ceiling. An 80%+ accuracy rate delivers compounding 
value across four additional dimensions:

- **Reduced rework** — Higher output quality means fewer correction cycles
- **Faster decisions** — Reliable AI-assisted insight compresses decision timelines
- **Capacity for innovation** — Time reclaimed from routine tasks is reallocated to high-value work
- **Competitive agility** — Faster analysis and development cycles relative to market peers

